reviewText: Juno is great! Just too bad they are no longer making videos.

My baby quickly loved Juno when she saw it on baby first tv I new I had to order it and I'm glad I did. The music is entertaining and it teaches baby count. My baby especially loves bunny and juno...I think its the braids.
Like all other Juno DVDs, this one was great.  My twins love it.  Plus, it addresses quite a few real-life "issues" that parents/kids face (haircuts, etc).

My children absolutely love the JUNO BABY / JR. series of dvd's and cd's.
Great for musical development in young children.
